description:
Reducing redness and acne-like bumps is easy with the careful application of the right products. Reduce redness and acne-like bumps with help from a celebrity makeup artist in this free video clip.

Expert: Kendra Richards
Contact: kendrarichards.com/
Bio: Kendra Richards is a professional makeup artist.
Filmmaker: Richard Benton

Series Description: You have to take a number of different things into consideration when choosing and applying makeup, like your hair color, your eye color and even the time of year. Get tips on how to apply and choose makeup with help from a celebrity makeup artist in this free video series.
title: How to Reduce Redness & Acne-Like Bumps
